      <h1 class="display-4 intro">
          What is JotDown?
      </h1>
      <p class="lead">
          JotDown is a simple and easy Task-Manager tool that allows its users to create, read, update and delete tasks. 
      </p>
      <h1 class="display-4 intro">
          Our Features!
      </h1>
      <p>
          <ul class="lead">
              <li>Users can create tasks by clicking on the <i class="fa fa-plus" style="cursor: pointer; font-size: 20px"></i> icon in the homepage, which requires description and status</li>
              <li>When a user logs in, all tasks are displayed automatically</li>
              <li>The 'options' option in the homepage allows users to customize the rendered tasks by filtering and sorting according to status or date of creation </li>
              <li>A task can be either deleted or updated by clicking on either of the icons <i class="fa fa-trash"></i> or <i class="far fa-edit"></i></li>
              <li>Users may wish to insert a profile picture or change their account's password directly in the <a href="profile" class="">Profile</a> section</li>
              <li>Any other concerns? Feel free to contact us by navigating directly to the <a href="contact" class="">Contact</a> section</li>
          </ul>
      </p>
